            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>inerviae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> A<supplied reason="lost">nton</supplied>in<supplied reason="lost">ia</supplied>nae <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">C</supplied>onstantiniu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>I <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptae</ex></expan> Fau<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>st</abbr><ex>ino</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>Ruf</abbr><ex>ino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ursprüngliche Aufstellung vermutlich im Fahnenheiligtum des Legionslagers (Lehner).</p>
            </div>
